Name: The Ragdoll
About the game: What is The Ragdoll? The Ragdoll is a fast-paced, action filled fighting game, which looks back to our childhood-favorite stickman fight games but with modern twists. In this game you'll have the chance to have fun either alone or with your friends and even with strangers. Features • Three different, themed tournaments • Dozens of unlockable skins • Dozens of different objects to fight with • 15+ unlockable maps • Local quick game and co-op tournaments • Online co-op tournaments and two PvP game modes, • Full controller support • 15+ achievements • Puns
